Object class is the parent class of all the classes by default . all the classes are inherited from the object class
toString() → Returns a string representation of the object.
equals(Object obj) → Compares two objects for logical equality.
hashCode() → Returns a unique integer hash value for the object.
getClass() → Returns the runtime class of the object.
clone() → Creates and returns a copy of the object.
finalize() → Called before an object is garbage collected (deprecated).
wait() → Causes current thread to wait until notified.
notify() → Wakes up one waiting thread.
notifyAll() → Wakes up all waiting threads.
